===Phrase===
'''[[bury]] [[the]] [[hatchet]]'''

# {{idiom}} To [[stop]] [[fighting]] or [[arguing]]; to reach an [[agree]]ment, or at least a [[truce]].
#:''They need to calm down and '''bury the hatchet''' before someone gets hurt.''

